flowchart TD
    A[Admin buka Dashboard Penjadwalan] --> B[Buat scheduler baru]
    B --> C[Pilih route dan shuttle]
    C --> D[Simpan DepartureScheduler]
    D --> E[Generate departure harian 90 hari]
    E --> F[Buka Jadwal Bus Harian]
    F --> G[Pilih departure]
    G --> H[Assign driver, driver2, crew, shuttle]
    H --> I[Isi master cost manifest]
    I --> J[Simpan manifest]
    J --> K{Siap dijual?}
    K -- Belum --> L[Status tetap INIT/DRIVER/SHUTTLE]
    K -- Ya --> M[Klik Release]
    M --> N[Remark RELEASE]
    N --> O[Departure visible untuk outlet]
